      "text": "こころとこころが喋ってるみたいですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "こころとこころが喋ってるみたいですわね……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8628311714,
      "endTime": 39.4425138077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "急にごめんなさい。唯さんは何をしてたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "急にごめんなさい。唯さんは何をしてたんですか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6358470839,
      "endTime": 43.389407197800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "konyui",
      "speakerName": "平沢唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "平沢唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-konyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-konyui002.m4a",
      "text": "私達は～、部室でお茶してるよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "私達は～、部室でお茶してるよ？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6027405025,
      "endTime": 47.9117202999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "konazusa",
      "speakerName": "中野梓",
      "speakerNameEn": "中野梓",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-konazusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-konazusa001.m4a",
      "text": "いっつもお茶ばっかり。今日こそ練習しますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いっつもお茶ばっかり。今日こそ練習しますよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1117203953,
      "endTime": 52.606142163499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "konyui",
      "speakerName": "平沢唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "平沢唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-konyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-konyui003.m4a",
      "text": "かたいこと言わないでよあずにゃん～\nそれで、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "かたいこと言わないでよあずにゃん～\nそれで、どうしたの？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7994754396,
      "endTime": 57.790019568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんの曲は、私達が普段歌うアイドルソングとは\nまた違う世界観だな、と感じましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "みなさんの曲は、私達が普段歌うアイドルソングとは\nまた違う世界観だな、と感じましたの",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9766862633,
      "endTime": 66.1747589828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "だから、普段みなさんがどうやって曲を作っているか\nどんな活動をしているのかを聞かせてくださらない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だから、普段みなさんがどうやって曲を作っているか\nどんな活動をしているのかを聞かせてくださらない？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3680920682,
      "endTime": 73.6475251279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "konyui",
      "speakerName": "平沢唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "平沢唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-konyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-konyui004.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、私達の活動か～\nこんな感じで毎日お茶してるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "う～ん、私達の活動か～\nこんな感じで毎日お茶してるよ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8608581943,
      "endTime": 81.73657230559999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
